



CHC Helicopter
























Menu

Flight Schedule







Making the World More Accessible
CHC Helicopter's unmatched helicopter services enable people around the world to go further, do more and come home safely.It demands our best—every moment, every day—even as we regularly raise the standards for what we do. Our global team is talented and passionate in providing offshore transportation to the oil-and-gas industry, flying search-and-rescue and emergency medical missions, and delivering maintenance/repair/overhaul and support services. Our capabilities are based on unique knowledge and accomplishment amassed from traveling out to and back from the world's most remote and challenging destinations.

View Restructuring Information Here

CHC CEO Karl Fessenden - Back to Basics: Prioritizing Safety in a Challenging EconomyIn keynote remarks at the 12th annual CHC Safety & Quality Summit, an internationally recognized aviation-safety event, CHC President and Chief Executive Officer Karl Fessenden discussed the importance of ensuring that safety continues to remain a top industry priority. 





CHC News



CHC Helicopter Celebrates 70 Years of Serving Customers around the World 
Jan 31, 2017
             -- CHC Group today announced the beginning of a year-long celebration of the operator’s 70-year history since its humble beginnings as a crop dusting operation in British Columbia in April of 1947. 
        

Vincent D’Rozario joins CHC Helicopter as Regional Director, Asia Pacific
Jan 30, 2017
             -- CHC Group announced that Vincent D’Rozario has joined the company as Regional Director, Asia Pacific.
        

CHC Australia Reaches 25,000 Hour Milestone on AW139
Jan 19, 2017
             -- CHC Group announced it had recently reached the 25,000 flight hour milestone on its fleet of AW139s in Australia.
        


