Company Profile
Sector: Energy
Industry: Oil, Gas & Coal
Sub-Industry: Oil & Gas Services & Equip
CHC Helicopter S.A. provides commercial operations of medium and heavy helicopters. The Company offers helicopter and logistics support, parts, and maintenance services. CHC Helicopter serves the offshore oil and gas industry worldwide.




