San Francisco Helicopter Tour with Napa Valley Landing and VIP Wine Tasting Experience - 3 Hours (FREE SHUTTLE SERVICE INCLUDED!)







Pair some of the best vines on the planet with some of the best views in the Bay.

  Union Square/Fisherman's Wharf (San Francisco)
 Available Dates












Item: SA16209N 




Our Price:

$435




 Lowest Price Guarantee
















OR













Safe, Secure Shopping 

















Description





Pair some of the best vines on the planet with some of the best views in the Bay. This helicopter wine tour is the apex of Napa Valley sightseeing.
Not only do you fly over the impressive vineyards but you also get to visit one of the Valley’s most prestigious houses and sample a few regional favorites! On top of all that, you’ll enjoy a thrilling chopper tour of the Bay Area, which includes marvelous overhead views of some of its most famous landmarks!

Begin with a helicopter tour of the San Francisco Bay.
See the Golden Gate Bridge and Alcatraz.
Make your way over Napa Valley’s lush hills.
Land at a nearby airport and from there you will be transported to begin your guided vineyard tour.
Learn all about the harvesting and wine making process.
Enjoy delicious pairings with the wine tasting.
Take in the pastoral scenery one last time before hopping back into the chopper.
Enjoy even more scenic views on the way home.

Take your love of wine to new heights with this three-hour excursion. It’s one of the most sought-after outings in all of Napa Valley!



Intensity: 4.0


AwesomeThis is getting to the pointy end. Heights, speed, endurance or a combination of all form part of this adventure. Be prepared to be challenged both physically and mentally. Bring that 'can do' attitude and maybe a change of clothes. You're about to get a taste of Serious Fun!



Intensity: 4.0







